# Luke 04:01
Jesus,
full of the Holy Spirit,
returned from the Jordan and was led by the Spirit into the wilderness

# Luke 04:02
for forty days,
being tempted by the devil.

He ate nothing in those days.

Afterward,
when they were completed,
he was hungry.

# Luke 04:03
The devil said to him,
``If you are the Son of God,
command this stone to become bread.''

# Luke 04:04
Jesus answered him,
saying,
``It is written,
‘Man shall not live by bread alone,
but by every word of God.’''

# Luke 04:05
The devil,
leading him up on a high mountain,
showed him all the kingdoms of the world in a moment of time.

# Luke 04:06
The devil said to him,
``I will give you all this authority and their glory,
